Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:10.43,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,The words will make you out 'n' out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:15.77,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,I'll spend the day your way
