Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:37.54,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,They make the children really ring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.88,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,I'll spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.55,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,Call it morning driving through the sound and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.51,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,In and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:51.93,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,In and around the lake
