Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.18,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:04.07,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.53,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.95,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:19.96,Lyrics 2,,0,0,0,,There with you
