Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:28.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seven years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Joestar steals the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:33.68,Secondary,,0,0,0,,I had a vision of something truly dreadful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't mind losing your arm then, do you?
